@node LifeTeam


	@{u}@{b}Introduction about the Life Team :@{ub}@{uu}



The Life Team is a small @{b}French programming group@{ub}, which has for main goal to distribute freeware proggyes, Shareware's (and why not commercial's ;-) on Amiga. Our programms are made with the powerfull Blitz Basic 2 by Acid Software. Our second goal is to make Blitz wellknown (mainly in France), because it is probably one of the best languages. @{"Contact" link  Adresses} us !




	@{u}@{b}Life Team programms:@{ub}@{uu}

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}W-Anim :@{ub}@{uu} An IFF anim in window viewer. It has lots of functions (frame rate, palette choose ...).

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}Insulte :@{ub}@{uu} A program that insults you ( french only at the moment :-( ) !!!

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}LTAssign :@{ub}@{uu} An AppIcon that assigns files you drop on it.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}IRT :@{ub}@{uu} Icon Replacement Tool, Icon Replacement Tool, an appicon to easily change your icons.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}SmallGrabber :@{ub}@{uu} A screen grabber with another superb GUI ;-)

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}AppSize :@{ub}@{uu} An AppIcon that tels you the size of the directory you launch on it.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}SmallPlayer :@{ub}@{uu} A small module player for low-memory amiga.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}IconPlayer :@{ub}@{uu} An AppIcon that plays music modules files you launch on it.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}IconAct :@{ub}@{uu} An AppIcon that identify files and launch utilities.

@{bg fill}   @{bg background} @{u}@{b}Searcher :@{ub}@{uu} A very complet file finder.

You can find all those programms  on your favourite aminet site or by your DP distributor.

@Endnode

